snippet.description:
Today‚Äôs Doodle celebrates jollof rice, a quintessential West African dish simmered in reduced tomatoes, onions, peppers and regional spices. Nigeria-based guest artist Haneefah Adam created the artwork and Senegalese jazz musician Herv√© Samb composed the music.

snippet.title: Can I Survive 100 Days in Hardcore Survival Mode? - Perfectly Balanced Skyrim Challenge #Attempt2
snippet.description:
Welcome back to skyrim! Where today we set out on a second attempt of an impossible challenge! Can you beat the survive 100 days in skyrim hardcore challenge? The rules are simple, Legendary difficulty skyrim with survival mode but the added twist that you are not allowed to equip any Armor or weapons. This is the hardest possible challenge skyrim can offer. You are effectively playing at 1 hp and almost anything will kill you and fail the run. Ontop of that in survival mode you must eat and sleep similarly to an indie survival game. You must also balance temperatures which in the cold northern lands of skyrim is rather impossible. 

Mod Pack Used: https://next.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/collections/jqd9zz

So sit back and watch as the spiffing brit tests to see if Skyrim is a perfectly balanced game with no exploits or surviving 100 days of skyrim hardcore is a task that is simply too impossible for this pro exploiter!

What you have seen here today is part of a fantastic perfectly balanced gameplay series on youtube where I go from game to game and break them with wacky exploits to gain things like unlimited gold and infinite money all in a fantastic montage. If you enjoyed this then be sure to check out more. The style is similar to RT game and callmekevin in parts. A large influence on this series has come from Valefisk and The Killian Experience.

snippet.description:
This is Episode 216 of Finnegan's Garage and it's time to say goodbye to Game Over. We are taking the boat apart to ready is for a cross-country trip home with its new owner. I'm definitely keeping the 711ci twin-turbo Sonny Leonard Racing Engines Hemi engine but the rest of the boat and trailer are leaving. Don't worry, there are some excellent tips and parts used in this video because, of course, nothing ever comes apart easily, even if it's only been together for a couple of years.
